---
import BaseLayout from '../../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Breadcrumbs from '../../../components/Breadcrumbs.astro';
import CTAButton from '../../../components/CTAButton.astro';
import { COMPANY_INFO } from '../../../utils/constants';

const lang = 'en';
const post = {
  title: 'Prime Mover Fleet 2026: 5+ Units Financing with 0% Down Payment',
  slug: 'prime-mover-fleet-2026-5-plus-units',
  excerpt: 'Finance 5+ prime mover fleet with 0% down payment. Fleet expansion financing for growing transport businesses. Fast approval for multiple trucks.',
  date: '2026-01-08',
  author: 'Ing Heng Credit Team',
  readTime: 6,
  category: 'Transport Vehicles',
  image: '/images/blog/prime-mover-financing.jpg'
};

const keywords = ['prime mover fleet', 'multiple truck financing', 'fleet expansion', '0% down payment', 'transport business'],
  breadcrumbItems = [
  { label: 'Home', href: '/en' },
  { label: 'Blog', href: '/en/blog' },
  { label: post.title, href: `/en/blog/${post.slug}` }
];
---

<BaseLayout title={post.title} description={post.excerpt} lang={lang} keywords={keywords}>
  <script type="application/ld+json">
    {
      "@context": "https://schema.org",
      "@type": "BlogPosting",
      "headline": post.title,
      "description": post.excerpt,
      "datePublished": post.date,
      "author": { "@type": "Organization", "name": post.author },
      "publisher": {
        "@type": "Organization",
        "name": "Ing Heng Credit & Leasing Sdn Bhd",
        "logo": {
          "@type": "ImageObject",
          "url": "https://inghengcredit.com/logo.png"
        }
      }
    }
  </script>

  <Breadcrumbs items={breadcrumbItems} />

  <article class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-12">
    <header class="mb-8">
      <span class="text-sm font-semibold" style="color: #D4A574;">Transport Vehicles</span>
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mt-2" style="color: #2D1810; font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif; text-transform: uppercase;">{post.title}</h1>
      <p class="text-gray-600 mt-4">{post.excerpt}</p>
      <div class="flex items-center gap-4 text-sm text-gray-500 mt-4">
        <span>{post.author}</span>
        <span>•</span>
        <time>{new Date(post.date).toLocaleDateString('en-US', { year: 'numeric', month: 'long', day: 'numeric' })}</time>
        <span>•</span>
        <span>{post.readTime} min read</span>
      </div>
    </header>

    <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
      <h2>Fleet Expansion: 5+ Prime Movers</h2>

      <p>Growing from single operator to fleet owner requires significant capital. 5 prime movers at RM180,000 each (used) = RM900,000 investment. Banks require RM90,000-RM180,000 down payment. Ing Heng Credit finances entire fleet with 0% down.</p>

      <h2>Fleet Financing Options</h2>

      <table>
        <thead>
          <tr>
            <th>Option</th>
            <th>Down Payment</th>
            <th>Monthly (5 trucks)</th>
            <th>Cash Preserved</th>
          </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr>
            <td>5 Used Trucks (RM180k each)</td>
            <td>RM0</td>
            <td>~RM11,000-RM13,000</td>
            <td>RM90,000-RM180,000</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>5 New Trucks (RM380k each)</td>
            <td>RM0</td>
            <td>~RM35,000-RM38,000</td>
            <td>RM190,000-RM380,000</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>10 Used Trucks (RM150k each)</td>
            <td>RM0</td>
            <td>~RM18,000-RM22,000</td>
            <td>RM150,000-RM300,000</td>
          </tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>

      <h2>Fleet Revenue Potential</h2>

      <h3>5 Prime Mover Fleet</h3>

      <p><strong>Normal Month:</strong>
  <br>• Revenue per truck: RM80,000
  <br>• Fleet revenue: RM400,000
  <br>• Operating costs: RM120,000
  <br>• Financing: RM12,000
  <br><strong>Net Profit: RM268,000 per month</strong></p>

      <p><strong>CNY Month:</strong>
  <br>• Revenue per truck: RM130,000
  <br>• Fleet revenue: RM650,000
  <br>• Operating costs: RM150,000
  <br>• Financing: RM12,000
  <br><strong>Net Profit: RM488,000 per month</strong></p>

      <h3>10 Prime Mover Fleet</h3>

      <p><strong>Normal Month:</strong> RM536,000 net profit</p>

      <p><strong>CNY Month:</strong> RM976,000 net profit</p>

      <h2>ROI: 5-Truck Fleet (Used)</h2>

      <p><strong>Investment:</strong> RM900,000 (0% down)</p>

      <p><strong>First Year:</strong>
  <br>• Normal months (11): RM2,948,000
  <br>• CNY month: RM488,000
  <br><strong>Total: RM3,436,000</strong></p>

      <p><strong>Payback:</strong> 3 months</p>

      <p><strong>First Year Profit:</strong> RM2,536,000</p>

      <h2>Fleet Expansion Strategy</h2>

      <h3>Phase 1: Start with 3 Used Trucks</h3>

      <p>• Investment: RM450,000
  <br>• Monthly profit: RM160,000
  <br>• Payback: 3 months
  <br>• Reinvest profits</p>

      <h3>Phase 2: Add 2 More Trucks</h3>

      <p>• Investment: RM360,000 (from profits)
  <br>• Fleet: 5 trucks
  <br>• Monthly profit: RM268,000</p>

      <h3>Phase 3: Expand to 10 Trucks</h3>

      <p>• Investment: RM750,000 (from profits)
  <br>• Fleet: 10 trucks
  <br>• Monthly profit: RM536,000</p>

      <h2>Benefits of Fleet Ownership</h2>

      <ul>
        <li><strong>Economies of Scale:</strong> Lower per-truck maintenance costs</li>
        <li><strong>Route Coverage:</strong> Serve multiple routes simultaneously</li>
        <li><strong>Backup Capacity:</strong> Absorb breakdowns without revenue loss</li>
        <li><strong>Negotiating Power:</strong> Better rates with fuel suppliers and clients</li>
        <li><strong>Business Value:</strong> Fleet increases company valuation</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Financing with 0% Down</h2>

      <p>Ing Heng Credit offers:
  <br>• 0% down payment on entire fleet
  <br>• 100% financing
  <br>• Used trucks (any age)
  <br>• Fast approval
  <br>• Flexible terms</p>

      <h2>Success Story</h2>

      <p>"Started with 3 used prime movers in 2023. 0% down payment, approved in fasts. Monthly profit RM150,000. After 6 months, added 2 more trucks with profits. After 1 year, expanded to 7 trucks. Now running 10-truck fleet with RM500,000+ monthly profit. 0% down let me start without draining working capital. Fleet paid off in 8 months total."</p>
      <p><em>— Rajendra Kumar, Fleet Owner</em></p>

      <div style="background: #F5F0E8; border-left: 4px solid #D4A574; padding: 1.5rem; margin: 2rem 0;">
        <h3 style="color: #2D1810; margin-top: 0;">Finance Your Fleet with 0% Down</h3>
        <p style="margin-bottom: 1rem;">5+ trucks financing. Approved in fasts.</p>
        <p style="margin-bottom: 0;"><strong>Contact:</strong> +60175700889 (WhatsApp) | 03-3324 8899 (Phone)</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <footer class="mt-12 pt-8 border-t">
      <CTAButton text="Get Fleet Financing" link={COMPANY_INFO.whatsapp.link} variant="accent" size="large" />
    </footer>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  h2 { color: #2D1810; font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif; text-transform: uppercase; font-size: 2rem; margin-top: 2.5rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; border-bottom: 3px solid #D4A574; padding-bottom: 0.5rem; }
  h3 { color: #8B6F47; font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif; text-transform: uppercase; font-size: 1.5rem; margin-top: 2rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem; }
  p { line-height: 1.8; color: #374151; }
  strong { color: #2D1810; font-weight: 700; }
  ul { list-style: none; padding-left: 0; }
  li { padding-left: 1.5rem; position: relative; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; line-height: 1.8; color: #374151; }
  li::before { content: '✓'; position: absolute; left: 0; color: #D4A574; font-weight: bold; }
  table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin: 1.5rem 0; }
  th { background: #2D1810; color: #F5F0E8; padding: 0.75rem; text-align: left; }
  td { border: 1px solid #E5E7EB; padding: 0.75rem; }
  em { display: block; margin-top: 0.5rem; color: #6B7280; font-style: normal; }
  br { display: none; }
</style>
